Title: Logwatch: Crash when using "\" in regular expression (e.g. windows paths)
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1608213818
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0b4

Windows paths include "\" as seperator but regex uses them as
escape character. Windows path backslashes need to be escaped to "\\\\".
